application.model

Class LocationObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.LocationObj

  • public class LocationObj
extends java.lang.Object
    This object creates a room, building, and campus object and retains the relationship between them while providing return methods for each objects simpleStringProperties, String values, and the object it's self. This object also calls setters for each object.
    Author:
    Patrick Scott Hadley
